<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-42-1131 </DOCNO><TEXT>The patent concerns a gamma tomography apparatus for medical diagnosis.The apparatus comprises a gamma scintillation camera head and a suspensionsystem for supporting and positioning the camera head with respect forthe patient. Both total body scanning and single photon emission tomographycan be carried out with the apparatus. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>